ools. Safe and Drug-Free Schools and Communities Act, State Grants, Guidance for State and Local Implementation of Programs. January 2004. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www.ed.gov/about/offices/list/osdfs/index.html\">http://www.ed.gov/about/offices/list/osdfs/index.html</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external free\" href=\"http://www2.ed.gov/about/offices/list/osdfs/index.html\">http://www2.ed.gov/about/offices/list/osdfs/index.html</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw1324\nCached time: 20180908030152\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.116 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.154 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 569/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 8703/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1822/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 12/40\nExpensive parser function count: 1/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 6196/5000000 bytes\nNumber of Wikibase entities loaded: 0/400\nLua time usage: 0.050/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 2.28 MB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  131.467      1 Template:Reflist\n100.00%  131.467      1 -total\n 49.35%   64.884      3 Template:Dead_link\n 34.56%   45.438      2 Template:Cite_web\n 29.61%   38.930      3 Template:Fix\n 26.32%   34.604      6 Template:Category_handler\n  3.67%    4.827      3 Template:Fix/category\n  1.56%    2.046      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:1630843-0!canonical and timestamp 20180908030152 and revision id 821965501\n -->\n</div>"},"langlinks":[{"lang":"nl","url":"https://nl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Drug-free_school_zone","langname":"Dutch","autonym":"Nederlands","*":"Drug-fr